This is a demo program for the proposed intents spec.

test with the following command.
intents-demo /path/to/config/file/your_config.conf

The format of the config file can be seen in demo.conf.

To add this item to pcmanfm, use the DES-EMA spec.
http://www.grumz.net/?q=node/377

A demo config file send_to.desktop is included here.
1. Put that file in ~/.local/share/file-manager/actions.
2. Edit the content of ~/.local/share/file-manager/actions/send_to.desktop, replace the config file on the Exec line with yours.
2. kill pcmanfm-qt, and restart it.
3. Select some files, and right click on them and you'll see the newly added popup menu item.

